│ Here, the *first transformation* means the *first transformation point* that modifies the IR in the pass         │
│ regardless of whether it's in the `autofix/build/llvm-build/125301/bin/opt -p loop-vectorize -mcpu=neoverse-v2   │
│ -force-vector-width=4 -S /tmp/reprod_ozxsx9n9.l` module or other modules.                                        │
